# Repo boundaries (benchmarks)

This repo is **wall-clock performance matrix + dashboard only**.

## Owns

- `catalog.toml`, `scripts/ingest/`, `data/latest/summary.json`
- `dashboard-next/` perf UI (pillars, matrix, bench detail)
- Sidecars: `benchmark-matrix.json`, `release-index.json`

## Never add here

- Proof corpus UI, voting board, `library.json`, `posture.json` → **proof-library**
- `proof-db/`, TOML entries, Lean bridge → **lic**
- Full lic/lis checkouts under `data/` → gitignored `data/workspaces/` for ephemeral agent runs only

## Cross-repo links

- `/proofs` redirects to https://proofs.lilangverse.xyz/
- Nav may link externally; do not re-import proof-library components or ingest scripts

## Ingest

Read sibling **lic** at CI via `LIC_ROOT` — do not vendor lic sources into this repo.
